多伦岛发生了异变，情况不明.Translation: Anomaly occurred on Toronto Island, situation unknown

洛丹伦命令我部前来查看.Translation: Lordaeron has ordered our unit to investigate

我们将以这座神庙为据点.Translation: We will use this temple as our stronghold

Level 1.Translation: Level 1, EN Translation: Allenw @ Ozlin server

诅咒者已被拾取.Translation: The Cursed item has been picked up

诅咒者附带高额减速，并废除人类的武器.Translation: The Cursed comes with a high slowdown effect and nullifies human weapons

范围直线 风已拾取.Translation: Straight Wind has been picked up

左键释放普通攻击.Translation: Left click to unleash a normal attack

第一开关已按下.Translation: The first switch has been toggled

最后开关已按下.Translation: The last switch has been toggled

为什么还有传送水晶，是谁在使用它.Translation: Why there are teleport crystals? Who is using them?

我们只有130s，速战速决.Translation: We only have 130 seconds, let's be quick about it

他就是这次异变的源头吗？.Translation: Is he the source of this anomaly?

总之，先击溃他吧.Translation: In any case, let's take him down first

收割者，僵尸神力拾取.Translation: Reaper, zombie divine power picked up

沿着洞穴瀑布向上.Translation: Climb up along the cave waterfall

抓紧离开这里吧.Translation: Let's hurry and leave this place

快上船离开这里.Translation: Hurry up and get on the boat to leave this place

Level 2.Translation: Level 2, EN Translation: Allenw @ Ozlin server

第二章_序幕.Translation: Chapter Two: Prologue, EN Translation: Allenw @ Ozlin server

鉴于之前的探索，这次的异变非同一般.Translation: Given the previous explorations, this anomaly is unusual

我们蒙受损失，必须撤退并向洛丹伦汇报情况.Translation: We have suffered losses; we must retreat and report to Lordaeron

一定会回来的，一定.Translation: We will definitely come back, definitely

这次我们将借道西边的洞穴，向洛丹伦撤退.Translation: This time we will retreat to Lordaeron through the cave to the west

那地方尘封多年，可能还会有守护者.Translation: That place has been sealed for years; there might still be guardians there

行动一定要万分小心.Translation: We must proceed with extreme caution

闪开，我们把一切挡路的障碍都炸开.Translation: Get out of the way; we're going to blow up everything blocking our path

这些石板年久失修了，小心点，士兵.Translation: These stone slabs have not been maintained for years; be careful, soldiers

20s后铁门破碎.Translation: The iron gate will break in 20 seconds

为什么有这么多机关，这里发生过什么？.Translation: Why are there so many mechanisms? What happened here?

20s后铁门打开.Translation: The iron gate will open in 20 seconds

20s后炸开墙壁.Translation: The wall will explode in 20 seconds

是前哨站，我们就快到了.Translation: It's a forward base; we're almost there

30s后炸开石头.Translation: The stones will explode in 30 seconds

是守护者，这老东西还在这里.Translation: It's the guardian; this old thing is still here

没办法了，强行突破.Translation: There's no other choice; we must force our way through

20s后开启传送.Translation: The teleport will open in 20 seconds

传送已经开启，快走.Translation: The teleport is open, hurry up!

感谢miluli提供的模型.Translation: Thanks to miluli for providing the model

他消失了，但我们仍被他玩弄于鼓掌之中.Translation: He has disappeared, but we are still being toyed with by him

25s后开启传送.Translation: The teleport will open in 25 seconds

增益者提升范围内恶灵的能力，强化身体体能.Translation: Enhancer increases the abilities of evil spirits within the range and strengthens their physical fitness.

WAD+右键施展地震波，击飞面前的僵尸.Translation: WAD + Right-click to unleash a shockwave, knocking back zombies in front.

SAWDAD+右键释放八方光刃(只有一次）.Translation: SAWDAD + Right-click to unleash the Eight-Direction Blade (only once).

这个山洞有些危险，等待兵力集结一并进入吧.Translation: This cave is a bit dangerous; let's wait for the troops to gather before entering.

道路已经通畅，我们出发.Translation: The road is clear; let's set off.

感谢miluli_提供的模型.Translation: Thanks to miluli_ for providing the model.

恶魔！他怎么会在这里，开枪击溃他.Translation: Demon! How could he be here? Shoot him down!

10s后门开.Translation: The door will open in 10 seconds.

那个恶魔一定在筹划着什么，决不能让他得逞.Translation: That demon must be plotting something; we cannot let him succeed.

因为恶魔的出现，我们的计划被彻底打乱.Translation: Our plan has been completely disrupted by the demon's appearance.

那家伙一定和这次的异变有关，十分危险.Translation: That guy must be related to this mutation; he's very dangerous.

我们放弃回到洛丹伦，再次来到这里.Translation: We gave up returning to Lordaeron and came back here again.

根据情报，恶魔就盘踞在岛屿的地下城内.Translation: According to intelligence, the demon is lurking in the underground city of the island.

我们要发动攻击，击败恶魔.Translation: We need to launch an attack and defeat the demon.

但愿这是最后一战，为了洛丹伦.Translation: I hope this is the final battle, for Lordaeron.

双子大门15s后打开.Translation: The Twin Gates will open in 15 seconds.

废弃的地下城仍在运行.Translation: The abandoned underground city is still operational.

20s铁门打开.Translation: The iron gate will open in 20 seconds.

解锁下一个大门，等待15s.Translation: Unlock the next gate, wait for 15 seconds.

解锁失败，大门被锁定.Translation: Unlock failed, the gate is locked.

访问成功，大门10s后开启.Translation: Access successful, the gate will open in 10 seconds.

道路被切断了，这是个阴谋.Translation: The road has been cut off; this is a conspiracy.

前方未知，但我们只能继续前进.Translation: Unknown ahead, but we can only move forward.

20s后大门打开.Translation: The gate will open in 20 seconds.

第一开关按下，解锁大门.Translation: First switch pressed, unlocking the gate.

大门即将锁闭，阻挡他们.Translation: The gate is about to close; block them.

第二开关已按下，解锁大门.Translation: Second switch pressed, unlocking the gate.

不要让他们穿过大门，坚持.Translation: Don't let them through the gate; hold firm.

大门5s后开启.Translation: The gate will open in 5 seconds.

又是他，为什么还活着.Translation: It's him again; why is he still alive?

暂时击退他了，快跑.Translation: We temporarily pushed him back; run!

40s后将对恶灵降下天罚.Translation: After 40 seconds, divine punishment will befall the evil spirit.

似乎有不洁者在干扰施法.Translation: It seems there are unclean beings interfering with the spell.

坚持住，我们以另一种方法转移.Translation: Hold on; we will transfer using another method.

10s后打开传送水晶.Translation: The teleport crystal will open in 10 seconds.

不要让僵尸靠近，10s后传送.Translation: Do not let the zombies get close; teleport in 10 seconds.

30s后石墙爆炸.Translation: The stone wall will explode in 30 seconds.

10s后门关.Translation: The door will close in 10 seconds.

门50s后开启.Translation: The door will open in 50 seconds.
